Please format a disk and name it "HIDEOUS" unpack the archive onto it,
install it and bootup, easy :) Please don't forget that this is just a
PD demo, the full game of HIDEOUS is available from the above address
or any official 5DL distributor (See Amiga Press) for only £2.95 +50p P&P

HIDEOUS will work on any 1MB Amiga, but an A1200 is recommended ;)


